OL,5,G0130 Horrors of the Black Museum
OL,6,     F1959. Horror. Director: Arthur
OL,7,     FCrabtree. Stars Michael Gough,
OL,8,     FJune Cunningham, Graham Curnow.
OL,9,     FAfter a series of murders, crime
OL,10,     Fwriter Edward Bancroft, is
OL,11,     Ffollowing events with particular
OL,12,     Finterest.
OL,13,G0310 Mites and Monsters 1938
OL,14,     F1938. An interesting short film
OL,15,     Fabout the variety of living
OL,16,     Fcreatures from small insects to
OL,17,     Flarge mammals.
